267
00:15:07,727 --> 00:15:09,718
Skinhead... Yes.

268
00:15:09,830 --> 00:15:12,958
It's a different story now.
The shoe's on the other foot.

269
00:15:13,567 --> 00:15:15,694
All right,
you had your chance then, Baxter.

