319
00:17:57,297 --> 00:17:58,730
- Huh?
- Teach it.

320
00:17:58,832 --> 00:18:02,563
Why, with all you know about golf,
you'd be a cinch to open a school.

321
00:18:02,836 --> 00:18:05,805
