00:21:07,187 --> 00:21:08,518
Excuse me.

349
00:21:10,957 --> 00:21:11,924
Hey!

350
00:21:43,556 --> 00:21:45,421
See you tonight, Lisa.

351
00:21:52,198 --> 00:21:53,825
Ma! Pop!

352
00:21:53,933 --> 00:21:55,730
Ma! Pop! Lisa!

353
00:21:55,835 --> 00:21:57,598
